contentrichtext.text: '''IBL''' is a [[three-letter acronym]] that may refer to: * ibuprofen lisinate * [[Image based lighting]] * [[InBound Links]] -- metric used by search engines * [[Inbred backcross lines]] * Indonesian Basketball League, former name of the [[National Basketball League (Indonesia)|National Basketball League]], the pre-eminent men's basketball league in Indonesia * [[Inquiry-based learning]] * [[Intercounty Baseball League]] * [[International Basketball League]] * [[International Basketball League (1999-2001)]] * [[International Brotherhood of Longshoremen]] * [[Ion beam lithography |Ion Beam Lithography]] * [[Serie A1 (baseball)|Italian Baseball League]] * [[Israel Baseball League]] * [[Instance-based learning]] (e.g. [[KNN]], [[PEL-C]], IBL-1, IBL-2 and IBL-3) * In before lock (of a [[Threaded discussion]]) * Involved But Looking * [[Indigo Bay Lodge Airport]], Mozambique (IATA code IBL) * [[International Business and Languages]] {{disambig}}
